        <updateDate>2020-05-19T18:01:13Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Judicial Travel Accountability Act </b></p> <p>This bill requires a judicial officer to annually disclose (1) the source, description, and value of certain gifts; (2) a detailed description of meetings and events attended, including the names of other known attendees; and (3) total expenses for transportation, lodging, and meals. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
